WEBVTT

00:00:02.887 --> 00:00:07.899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

00:00:07.900 --> 00:00:12.499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:13.999
♪By your side once♪

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

00:00:17.075 --> 00:00:21.049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

00:00:21.050 --> 00:00:25.970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

00:00:25.987 --> 00:00:30.699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:35.261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

00:00:35.262 --> 00:00:40.445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

00:00:40.725 --> 00:00:43.086
=Shall We Dance=

00:00:43.087 --> 00:00:46.182
=Episode 17=

00:00:49.820 --> 00:00:52.220
(Revenge is your fate.)

00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:56.659
(You must kill every last one of them.)

00:00:56.660 --> 00:00:57.780
Xiao Man.

00:01:00.500 --> 00:01:02.180
I know you are not asleep.

00:01:15.860 --> 00:01:18.660
Xiao Man, I have a question.

00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:20.740
Your Majesty, please ask.

00:01:22.700 --> 00:01:24.219
Today, at court,

00:01:24.220 --> 00:01:25.340
thank you.

00:01:26.940 --> 00:01:30.340
But where did that edict come from?

00:01:30.460 --> 00:01:31.980
It was like a magic trick.

00:01:33.020 --> 00:01:34.260
What magic trick?

00:01:34.500 --> 00:01:36.300
I quietly rewrote one.

00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:39.540
Then could it be

00:01:39.700 --> 00:01:40.859
that day in the Imperial Study,

00:01:40.860 --> 00:01:42.340
you were there for this edict?

00:01:42.540 --> 00:01:43.660
Yes.

00:01:45.500 --> 00:01:46.900
You did it to help me.

00:01:47.780 --> 00:01:48.900
No.

00:01:56.020 --> 00:01:57.580
I still have another question.

00:01:59.540 --> 00:02:00.819
I have seen your ability

00:02:00.820 --> 00:02:02.620
to remember everything at a glance.

00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:05.300
But how was the handwriting
exactly the same?

00:02:07.620 --> 00:02:10.459
You taught me my writing,
stroke by stroke.

00:02:10.460 --> 00:02:11.940
Of course it was easy to imitate.

00:02:12.940 --> 00:02:14.420
Do you not remember?

00:02:17.350 --> 00:02:23.620
(Light)

00:02:29.380 --> 00:02:30.500
That is right.

00:02:31.340 --> 00:02:33.780
Back then, just to avoid
the Grand Tutor's assignments,

00:02:34.620 --> 00:02:36.980
we each wrote half.

00:02:39.380 --> 00:02:41.299
Since Your Majesty has finished asking,

00:02:41.300 --> 00:02:42.740
please return.

00:02:43.420 --> 00:02:44.540
I will not leave.

00:02:47.500 --> 00:02:48.620
I will not leave.

00:02:52.260 --> 00:02:53.300
Xiao Man.

00:02:55.380 --> 00:02:56.900
Xiao Man, you do not want me anymore.

00:02:57.700 --> 00:02:59.020
Xiao Man.

00:03:01.860 --> 00:03:03.380
It is so cold outside.

00:03:04.060 --> 00:03:05.180
Xiao Man.

00:03:07.420 --> 00:03:08.540
Xiao Man.

00:03:57.020 --> 00:03:58.140
Xiao Man.

00:03:58.500 --> 00:04:00.700
I know your heart is on my side.

00:04:00.820 --> 00:04:02.540
Let us not go on like this, all right?

00:04:03.220 --> 00:04:04.899
Every duty assigned by Your Majesty,

00:04:04.900 --> 00:04:06.940
I have fulfilled without fail.

00:04:07.220 --> 00:04:09.660
I have never let personal feelings
interfere with my duty.

00:04:21.260 --> 00:04:22.460
You feel a bit warm.

00:04:23.100 --> 00:04:24.820
You may have caught a chill.

00:04:25.740 --> 00:04:27.820
You have ignored me for days.

00:04:28.420 --> 00:04:30.139
Compared with physical discomfort,

00:04:30.140 --> 00:04:31.780
this hurts my heart even more.

00:04:33.620 --> 00:04:35.220
A fever is nothing.

00:04:41.340 --> 00:04:42.460
Xiao Man.

00:04:43.540 --> 00:04:44.739
Between the two of us,

00:04:44.740 --> 00:04:46.780
can we stop holding this distance?

00:04:47.060 --> 00:04:49.660
Please do not put me
in a difficult position, Your Majesty.

00:04:50.820 --> 00:04:51.940
Xiao Man.

00:04:54.340 --> 00:04:55.780
What is this?

00:04:57.940 --> 00:04:59.300
Is that not me?

00:05:09.180 --> 00:05:10.300
Xiao Man.

00:05:10.780 --> 00:05:13.020
That knot we cannot untie...

00:05:17.260 --> 00:05:18.740
Let time settle it.

00:05:23.020 --> 00:05:25.060
You must keep the court stable.

00:05:25.540 --> 00:05:27.660
I must see old wrongs set right.

00:05:28.980 --> 00:05:29.939
Then let us wait

00:05:29.940 --> 00:05:31.900
for change to bring an opening.

00:05:32.580 --> 00:05:34.180
If we stay stuck here,

00:05:34.980 --> 00:05:36.700
neither of us will be free.

00:05:38.300 --> 00:05:39.420
Xiao Man.

00:05:41.100 --> 00:05:42.700
You have always given way for me,

00:05:43.460 --> 00:05:45.340
yet I have failed you time and again.

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:49.020
Tomorrow night,

00:05:49.660 --> 00:05:51.620
I will take you to see something.

00:05:52.780 --> 00:05:53.900
See what?

00:05:54.420 --> 00:05:56.100
A secret for now.

00:05:57.500 --> 00:05:59.380
At the very least,

00:05:59.420 --> 00:06:01.820
there is one thing I can say

00:06:02.900 --> 00:06:06.220
to you without any guilt.

00:06:47.140 --> 00:06:48.419
You are still ill.

00:06:48.420 --> 00:06:49.699
You should not eat too much.

00:06:49.700 --> 00:06:51.300
Just this small piece.

00:06:55.060 --> 00:06:56.180
You eat as well.

00:07:01.700 --> 00:07:02.979
This mooncake is too big.

00:07:02.980 --> 00:07:05.180
Let us call Duanmu Zhi
and the others to share it.

00:07:07.700 --> 00:07:09.300
This is a reunion mooncake.

00:07:09.460 --> 00:07:11.100
It is meant only for the two of us.

00:07:11.775 --> 00:07:12.975
Go on, eat it.

00:07:19.420 --> 00:07:20.540
Hurry and eat.

00:07:20.620 --> 00:07:22.300
Afterward, I will take you somewhere.

00:07:48.420 --> 00:07:51.220
Is this not the unfinished
replica of Yanbo Parlor?

00:07:51.260 --> 00:07:52.339
It is.

00:07:52.340 --> 00:07:55.060
As an emperor known only for indulgence,

00:07:55.220 --> 00:07:56.980
I must come by from time to time.

00:08:00.380 --> 00:08:02.140
So our visit tonight

00:08:02.380 --> 00:08:03.939
to outsiders,

00:08:03.940 --> 00:08:06.420
is nothing more
than a routine inspection.

00:08:07.060 --> 00:08:09.020
Your Majesty.

00:08:09.340 --> 00:08:10.580
You may all rise.

00:08:16.620 --> 00:08:17.740
Xiao Man.

00:08:18.300 --> 00:08:19.420
Come with me.

00:08:26.820 --> 00:08:28.180
This Yanbo Parlor

00:08:28.380 --> 00:08:30.660
is the place that truly belongs to us.

00:08:30.820 --> 00:08:32.339
Is this what Your Majesty meant

00:08:32.340 --> 00:08:34.300
by a sight you can face
with a clear conscience?

00:08:34.420 --> 00:08:35.620
Of course not.

00:08:37.140 --> 00:08:38.020
Come.

00:08:56.500 --> 00:08:57.419
These here

00:08:57.420 --> 00:08:58.579
are elite troops concealed

00:08:58.580 --> 00:09:01.260
behind performers' rehearsals
and craftsmen's work.

00:09:02.900 --> 00:09:05.460
Others believe
Great Qian's forces are weak,

00:09:05.660 --> 00:09:08.940
never knowing that my aunt and I
have trained our own army in secret.

00:09:09.940 --> 00:09:12.259
These soldiers rotate day and night.

00:09:12.260 --> 00:09:13.059
One group by day,

00:09:13.060 --> 00:09:14.339
another by night.

00:09:14.340 --> 00:09:15.620
No one would imagine

00:09:15.860 --> 00:09:17.019
that my army

00:09:17.020 --> 00:09:19.100
trains within the palace itself.

00:09:20.500 --> 00:09:21.620
Xiao Man.

00:09:22.300 --> 00:09:23.419
For the people at the borders,

00:09:23.420 --> 00:09:25.100
I have prepared with all my strength.

00:09:25.380 --> 00:09:26.579
Everything you have sacrificed,

00:09:26.580 --> 00:09:28.340
every effort you have made,

00:09:28.460 --> 00:09:30.220
will not be in vain.

00:09:32.300 --> 00:09:33.860
Their numbers seem small.

00:09:34.100 --> 00:09:36.700
Can they face the fierce foreign troops?

00:09:36.740 --> 00:09:38.260
This is not all of them.

00:09:39.300 --> 00:09:42.059
Beyond Yanbo Parlor in the palace,
some soldiers were placed by my aunt

00:09:42.060 --> 00:09:44.820
in locations disguised
as her extravagant pursuits.

00:09:45.700 --> 00:09:48.300
But this unit is the most exceptional.

00:09:50.660 --> 00:09:53.500
They know the border tactics inside out.

00:10:00.420 --> 00:10:01.940
Because they are

00:10:02.180 --> 00:10:04.259
the former troops and descendants of

00:10:04.260 --> 00:10:06.139
the force that once swept the frontiers,

00:10:06.140 --> 00:10:09.740
led by General Xiao Congrong.

00:10:19.140 --> 00:10:20.780
I know what you are thinking.

00:10:20.980 --> 00:10:21.899
When my aunt and I

00:10:21.900 --> 00:10:23.179
rebuilt this force,

00:10:23.180 --> 00:10:24.500
we did consider

00:10:24.580 --> 00:10:26.380
whether resentment might linger.

00:10:26.820 --> 00:10:29.420
But every one of these soldiers
has remained devoted to their duty,

00:10:30.220 --> 00:10:31.260
all to

00:10:31.540 --> 00:10:32.499
defend the lands

00:10:32.500 --> 00:10:34.660
once secured by the Xiao Army.

00:10:36.140 --> 00:10:38.420
General Xiao Congrong's righteousness

00:10:39.140 --> 00:10:40.780
has never been lost.

00:10:52.980 --> 00:10:55.980
Deputy General Li Qing of the Xiao Army
pays my respects to Your Majesty.

00:10:57.175 --> 00:10:58.957
(Shangguan Qing)

00:10:59.050 --> 00:11:00.757
(Li Qing)

00:11:01.220 --> 00:11:02.380
Paying respects...

00:11:14.580 --> 00:11:15.700
Xiao Man.

00:11:17.340 --> 00:11:19.100
I want to give you something.

00:11:25.740 --> 00:11:27.340
She looks just like...

00:11:37.620 --> 00:11:38.580
Your Majesty,

00:11:38.700 --> 00:11:40.580
General Xiao's mount in those years

00:11:40.780 --> 00:11:42.580
was a rare and exceptional steed.

00:11:43.740 --> 00:11:45.019
This is its descendant,

00:11:45.020 --> 00:11:46.620
one of the finest of its kind.

00:11:49.460 --> 00:11:51.779
Today, it returns to where it belongs,

00:11:51.780 --> 00:11:54.260
presented to Miss Zhen Mujun.

00:11:55.500 --> 00:11:58.339
May you enjoy the bloom of your youth,

00:11:58.340 --> 00:11:59.780
joyful on your birthday,

00:11:59.820 --> 00:12:01.099
as constant as the moon,

00:12:01.100 --> 00:12:02.540
year after year.

00:12:03.420 --> 00:12:04.860
How did you know?

00:12:05.940 --> 00:12:07.780
I searched the records carefully.

00:12:07.860 --> 00:12:09.500
Your name, Xiao Man,

00:12:09.740 --> 00:12:10.860
made me think

00:12:11.100 --> 00:12:13.060
of the fullness of the moon.

00:12:16.740 --> 00:12:17.900
Do you know

00:12:18.060 --> 00:12:19.979
why it always rains on the fifteenth day

00:12:19.980 --> 00:12:21.179
of the eighth month?

00:12:21.180 --> 00:12:22.260
Why?

00:12:22.900 --> 00:12:24.899
Because my parents and family

00:12:24.900 --> 00:12:27.180
all died on that day.

00:12:27.820 --> 00:12:29.059
And I

00:12:29.060 --> 00:12:30.659
will never be complete again.

00:12:30.660 --> 00:12:31.780
Xiao Man.

00:12:32.500 --> 00:12:34.019
Zhen Mujun of the Zhen family

00:12:34.020 --> 00:12:36.379
was destined twenty years past
to be Chu Ying's Empress.

00:12:36.380 --> 00:12:36.779
Chu Ying.

00:12:36.780 --> 00:12:37.460
I...

00:12:38.260 --> 00:12:39.380
Look.

00:12:40.620 --> 00:12:42.220
The rain has stopped,

00:12:42.460 --> 00:12:45.620
but the road ahead is still clouded.

00:12:48.660 --> 00:12:49.860
I believe

00:12:50.220 --> 00:12:51.500
that one day,

00:12:52.460 --> 00:12:54.860
the clouds will part
and the moon will appear.

00:13:02.620 --> 00:13:04.620
I want to ride alone for a while.

00:13:07.260 --> 00:13:08.340
Xiao Man.